 -- ------------- -- --------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
 /*             1 */ [RULE_KEY] int   ,                                                                                                                                                                                                                                       
 /*             2 */ [FGS_CODE] varchar(20)   ,                                                                                                                                                                                                                               
 /*             3 */ [RULESET_CODE] char(5) NULL,                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    
 /*             4 */ [PO_FGC_KEY] int   ,                                                                                                                                                                                                                                     
 /*             5 */ [REQ_FGC_KEY] int   ,                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    
 /*             6 */ [TOLERANCE_TYPE] char(2) NULL,                                                                                                                                                                                                                                  
 /*             7 */ [GRP_KEY] int NULL,                                                                                                                                                                                                                                             
 /*             8 */ [ALLOW_ADVANCE_WORKFLOW] char(1)   ,                                                                                                                                                                                                                     
 /*             9 */ [MSG_KEY] int NULL,                                                                                                                                                                                                                                             
 /*            10 */ [IS_ACTIVE] char(1)   ,                                                                                                                                                                                                                                  
 /*            11 */ [SYNC_GUID] binary(16)   ,                                                                                                                                                                                                                               
 /*            12 */ [LAST_MODIFIED] nvarchar(255)   )
